Author: Jocelyn Alsdorf
Program name: Word-Checker
Description: This app allows a user to input a word and a sentence.
The sentence is then checked for instances of their inputted word
and the number of times the word was repeated in their sentence is given.
Set-up Instructions:
Ruby
The gems used:
gem('sinatra')
gem('sinatra-contrib')
gem('rspec')
gem('capybara')
gem('pry')

To play, enter a word and a sentence into the inputs and click the send button.


